# CSS Patterns

## Structure
- Global styles in `src/styles/`
- Component-specific styles scoped in `.astro` files
- Follow existing file organization

## Tailwind Usage
- Prefer Tailwind utilities over custom CSS
- Use `@apply` sparingly - only for complex patterns
- Define custom utilities in `tailwind.config.js`
- Use semantic color names from theme

## Custom Properties
- Use CSS custom properties for dynamic values
- Namespace custom properties: `--auxo-*`
- Define in `:root` or component scope
- Support dark mode with `.dark` class

## Performance
- Minimize unused CSS
- Avoid deep nesting (max 3 levels)
- Use PostCSS optimizations
- Keep selector specificity low
